data.description: Affordable 2 bedroom, 1 bath home with attached garage in perfect location near Downtown Lemont, shopping, dining & Metra Station. Features: A large living room with luxury vinyl plank flooring; Kitchen with all appliances; Bedroom with door to the deck overlooking the tree-lined yard; Master bedroom with original hardwood flooring; Large, walk-in attic could be finished for additional space; Partially finished basement; 2 car tandem attached garage. Original hardwood flooring under LVP. Roof & siding (2023), AC (2016), Furnace (2014), Water heater (2022).
